## 🚀 Free Cloud Deployment (Render + Vercel)

✅ **Prep complete** - Builds JAR/static files, prod CORS, API proxy.

### Backend (Render - free tier)
1. render.com → New Web Service → GitHub repo: divy151005/UniAgent-Teams-Integrated-University-ERP-Bot
2. Dir: `/backend`, Java runtime, build `mvn clean package -DskipTests`, start `java -jar target/erp-agent-1.0.0.jar`
3. Backend API: `https://[your-app].onrender.com/api`

### Frontend (Vercel - free)
1. vercel.com → Import repo, dir `/frontend`, Vite preset
2. Add env `VITE_API_URL=https://[your-backend].onrender.com`
3. Frontend: `https://[your-app].vercel.app`

**Live Demo URLs:**
- Frontend: [TBD]
- Backend API: [TBD]
- H2 Console: [backend]/h2-console (local only)

**Notes:** H2 DB resets on restart (free tier sleeps). Upgrade PostgreSQL for persistence.

